MALACAÑANG MANILA

PROCLAMATION NO. 68

RESERVING FOR BARANGAY HOUSING SITE PURPOSES A CERTAIN PARCEL OF LAND OF THE PUBLIC DOMAIN SITUATED IN BARANGAY CAASINAN, MUNICIPALITY OF CABADBARAN, PROVINCE OF AGUSAN DEL NORTE, ISLAND OF MINDANAO

Upon recommendation of the Secretary of Environment and Natural Resources, and by virtue of the powers vested in me by law, I, GLORIA MACAPAGAL-ARROYO, President of the Philippines, do hereby set aside a certain parcel of land of the public domain as barangay housing site, subject to private rights if any, for disposition under Chapter IX of the Public Land Law (Act No. 141), situated in Barangay Caasinan, Municipality of Cabadbaran, Province of Agusan del Norte, Island of Mindanao and more particularly described as follows:

Consolidation of Lots 2925, 5881, 2930, 2926, 2990, 2978 all of Cad 866, Cabadbaran Cadastre

Bounded on the NW., along lines 1-5 by a Creek; lines 5-7 by Lot 2986; Cad-866; on the N., along line 7-8 by lot 1820, Cad-905; on the NE., along lines 8-10 by lot 2991 and lot 2984; lines 10-12 by lot 2977; line 12-13 by lot 2973; on the SE., along lines 13-19 by Caasinan River; on the SW., along line 19-20 by lot 2934; line 20-21 by lot 2933; line 21-22 by lot 2931; line 22-23 by lot 2944; line 23-24 by lot 2927; line 24-25 by lot 2924; lines 25-27 by lot 2948; line 27-28 by lot 2947; line 28-29 by lot 2915; lines 29-32 by Opagan River; line 32-33 by lot 5879, all of the same cadastre; lines 33-49-50-1 by Opagan River. Beginning from point marked “1” on the plan being N. 34 deg. 35’W., 2501.45 meters from BLLM 1 of Cad 866, thence;

